data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 4 bedroom 2 bath home located in Grovetown, Georgia. This home boasts an open floor plan and a split bedroom plan, providing ample space for everyone. The big lot and huge yard are perfect for outdoor activities and entertainment. The neighborhood amenities include a pool, trails, sidewalks and more! This property is conveniently located near Fort Gordon and Columbia County shopping. Don't miss out on this opportunity.
